title: Sad Beautiful Tragic (Taylor's Version)
description:
This beautiful song sounds like it could go on Folklore.. And Ana has a lyrical theory that totally works! Who inspired this song and what has Taylor said about it? We take a deep dive into this hauntingly beautiful song!
What did we miss? What would you like to hear from us? There are lots of ways to reach us!
